Loop Different Ingredients for Condition vs Decrement.

Per the Chef spec, a loop checks the ingredient named in its START statement
before every pass; the ingredient named in the "until" statement is only
decremented. Here the body lowers 'condition' from 3 to 0 through the 2nd
mixing bowl, while the until statement decrements 'tally' from 9. After the
loop, tally is 6 and is served.

Ingredients.
3 g condition
9 g tally
1 g unit

Method.
Beat the condition.
Put condition into 2nd mixing bowl.
Remove unit from 2nd mixing bowl.
Fold condition into 2nd mixing bowl.
Beat the tally until beaten.
Put tally into mixing bowl.
Pour contents of the mixing bowl into the baking dish.

Serves 1.
